NeverRanked Source-Available License v1
========================================

Copyright (c) 2026 Lance Roylo

This license is modeled on the Business Source License pattern used
by MariaDB, Sentry, CockroachDB, and others. It is written in plain
language for clarity. For commercial deployments where you need a
court-tested license, we recommend swapping in the standard BSL 1.1
text from https://mariadb.com/bsl11/ with the same parameters
declared below; this plain-language version is intended to make the
intent obvious to anyone reading the repo.


What you CAN do with this code
------------------------------

- Read every line.
- Audit it. Fork it. Run it on a laptop. Run it on a staging server.
- Use it for personal projects, internal tools, evaluation,
  research, education, and security review.
- Copy ideas, patterns, and approaches into your own work.
- Cite this repository in writing, talks, or research.
- Open issues, submit pull requests, suggest improvements.


What you CANNOT do with this code
---------------------------------

You may not use this code, in whole or in substantial part, to
operate a commercial AEO Service.

An "AEO Service" is any commercial offering that allows third
parties (other than your own employees and contractors) to access
the functionality of this Licensed Work for any of:

  - AI citation tracking across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, Claude,
    or comparable answer engines
  - Schema completeness grading or JSON-LD quality scoring
  - Citation drift detection between time windows
  - Authority signal auditing (trust profiles, author bios)
  - Reddit citation tracking
  - Industry benchmark percentile reporting
  - Quarterly roadmap refresh from citation data
  - Any other primary functionality of NeverRanked as offered at
    https://neverranked.com

If you want to operate a commercial AEO Service using this code, you
must obtain a separate commercial license from the Licensor. Contact
licensing@neverranked.com.


