Change Date and Sunset to MIT
-----------------------------

Change Date:    2030-04-29
Change License: MIT License

On the Change Date, the restrictions in the "What you CANNOT do"
section above are removed and this code becomes available under the
MIT License. This means: 4 years after the publication of this code,
anyone is free to use it for any purpose, including operating a
competing AEO Service.

This sunset is deliberate. The intent of the restriction is to give
the original Licensor a fair window to build a business on this
work, not to lock the code up forever.


